                <div class="span12">
                  <h2 class="red-title"><span>1. Purpose of Charter</span></h2>
                  <p>The Board Charter sets out of the role, composition and responsibilities of the Board of Directors ("the Board") of Far East Holdings Berhad ("the Company").</p>
                  <!--<ul class="list icons">
                  	<li><i class="icon-ok"></i> A strategic guidance and effective oversight of management;</li>
