                        <div class="span12">
                             <h2 class="red-title">7. Review of the Board Charter</h2>
							 <p>The Board Charter will be reviewed periodically by the Board to ensure its relevance in assisting the Board to discharge its duties with the changes in the corporate laws and regulations that may arise from time to time and to remain consistent with the Board's objectives and responsibilities.</p>

                        </div>

                    </div>
